Package com.gcu.agms.repository.impl

Class JdbcMaintenanceRecordRepository

java.lang.Object
com.gcu.agms.repository.impl.JdbcMaintenanceRecordRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
MaintenanceRecordRepository
@Repository public class JdbcMaintenanceRecordRepository extends Object implements MaintenanceRecordRepository
JDBC implementation of the MaintenanceRecordRepository interface. This class handles data access operations for maintenance records using Spring JDBC.
